"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"aeed571ef834a155f043eea5de6276f839066238","tid":861952,"uid":50310,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T13:50:29.000Z","msg":"講乜先得格？<br />\n可否用啲廢老都聽得明既說話<br />\n令佢地表態！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T14:37:19.000Z","msg":"首先可以強調佢地以前捱足幾十年 香港過去發展得咁快佢地都有份出力 庫房既錢係佢地有份貢獻既 而家政府就係將佢地幾十年黎既血汗錢倒曬落海 <br />\n有拎政府生果金或者其他津貼既就可以強調政府寧願拎啲錢去填海都唔會拎少少出黎加多啲錢俾佢地 完全唔尊重佢地為香港付出過 覺得佢地好唔抵<br />\n老人家唔多唔少都會覺得自己以前既付出對社會幾咁重要 呢個講法至少滿足左佢地個優越感 <br />\n之後就睇佢地著緊啲咩去講<br />\n例如有排政府醫院服務既 可以話啲錢如果可以俾少少醫院 已經可以等佢地排期覆診或者睇醫生做手術唔使等咁耐 去醫院排隊覆診唔使等成大半日先見到醫生 而家就係將可以俾醫院既錢倒落海 搞到佢地繼續排咁耐"},{"pid":"b65cf4153d80a0e9827ac6b5fae311643e27e7b3","tid":861952,"uid":60398,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T14:44:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>各位巴絲 唔理你依加喺屋企又好 定喺美國領事館 一齊去美國領事嘅Facebook 同 Twitter 留言洗版！</strong></span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/317451486051/posts/10156920430356052/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F317451486051%2Fposts%2F10156920430356052%2F&d=TqJSYLXMWS6ujcf1pnLk0DQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=de394bf6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/317451486051/posts/10156920430356052/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://mobile.twitter.com/usainhkmacau\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmobile.twitter.com%2Fusainhkmacau&d=TqJSYLXMWS6ujcf1pnLk0DQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=75d13e61\" target=\"_blank\">https://mobile.twitter.com/usainhkmacau</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"> 各位鍵盤戰士 出唔到嚟嘅你都可以做到嘢！</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">最好tag埋侵侵！</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"90d466523c686aa5a6d0a0db07767cd56492eb22","tid":861952,"uid":49508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"repl